title: Fire & Blood: Queens & Lions & Dragons
description:
Edited audio from the livestream on Jan 29th 2019. Guests are Eliana (Girls Gone Canon, Maester Monthly) and Michal Schick (Vassals of Kingsgrave, Hypable, HoW voices). We take a very deep character dive into Alyssa Velaryon, Alyssa Targaryen, and Rhaena Targaryen. There are a lot of parallels to Cersei, Catelyn, plus a discussion of Tyrion Targaryen!
